                If you are thinking about donating blood, follow the following steps:
                </p>
             <p>• Check if you are eligible.</p>
             <p>(as a blood donor)</p>
             <p>•	Find the nearest blood donation center.</p>
             <p>•	Book an appointment for a date and time depending on your availability and preference.</p>
             <p>•	Donate.</p>
            <p>For details about what you need to do before and after donating, visit Australian Red Cross Blood Service website below.</p>
          
            <a href="http://www.donateblood.com.au/learn/before-and-after-you-donate" target="_blank" class="btn btn-success btn-lg">Visit Red Cross Center website</a>
        </div>
    
        <div class="col-sm-5" style="margin-left:100px;">
